{"tid":1736521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家醒下啦 唔好覺得要救哂所有人先叫成功得唔得","createTime":"2019-11-18T18:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T06:04:09.000Z","uid":218097,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf7148ad321beff057f7f8d1de0f394af494c09","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:10:56.000Z","msg":"唔岩聽都係咁講<br />\n為左救around 百幾人 出面比人拉左遠遠超過呢個數<br />\n我唔係話唔洗救人 <br />\n<br />\n而家得兩個選擇<br />\n<br />\n繼續打落去 直到救哂所有人為止 vs 而家散水 以最少傷亡結束今日<br />\n<br />\n前者失敗結果 就係極多人比人拉 運動立即收皮<br />\n琴日風向就係一個都走唔到 今日已經有人走到出黎<br />\n唔好比感情影響到自己太多啦 手足們  無人想放棄poly<br />\n大家都係自己人 但為左救個堆人 一直有人比人拉<br />\n真係值得？<br />\n<br />\n一句：當人係condom? <br />\n就大於一切？ 係咪場運動完左都無所謂？<br />\n只要無人當poly係condom<br />\n<br />\n唔洗屌我冷氣軍師 事實係難接受 你地為左要唔當人係condom而繼續犧牲大量手足，同啲遊行畫面撚有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n今次poly事件完左 真係唔好再打陣地 求下大家<br />\n<br />\n最後 尊重大家決定 仲有請唔好再屌poly入面既人投降<br />\n入面既感受 出面既人係唔會體會得到 由奇係有咁多16歲以下既手足"},{"pid":"62ce2089d5788a30700d633c80a4da62f56c83c5","tid":1736521,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:12:39.000Z","msg":"唔好俾感情帶領住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1f2645943db740f7b4fb53ea1dc9c62e29067f","tid":1736521,"uid":263273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:14:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 入面點會得百幾人"},{"pid":"877f14da33e98eda5a351c103cd2eb3a6b9428ba","tid":1736521,"uid":262043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"救人成本好大<br />\n大到成個運動既生死<br />\n如果依個運動輸咗<br />\n之前幾百個被檢控既手足就變condom"},{"pid":"9e886d9cfdc4f0bc97e69aa66a69f7b5adcd44d6","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f1f2645943db740f7b4fb53ea1dc9c62e29067f","tid":1736521,"uid":263273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:14:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 入面點會得百幾人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:20:00.000Z","msg":"你呢啲同我係出面見到堆爛仔手足有咩分別<br />\n一黎就屌人老母 自己上tg睇 around 200個"},{"pid":"bfdf91a8fa942ec0942509fe375ad521dcf344f9","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"877f14da33e98eda5a351c103cd2eb3a6b9428ba","tid":1736521,"uid":262043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"救人成本好大<br />\n大到成個運動既生死<br />\n如果依個運動輸咗<br />\n之前幾百個被檢控既手足就變condom"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:20:36.000Z","msg":"救到人 但運動收皮<br />\n救唔到人 留力再戰 都仲有機會贏"},{"pid":"2b88675ce9ff646bb9d952d61a72cb9f850fbefc","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:22:29.000Z","msg":"唔撚洗屌我啦 我自己夢遊打機都係企前面<br />\n但有時侯真係要冷靜少少諗下<br />\n<br />\n亦無謂拎中大同理大去比"},{"pid":"b7038f843d05627fd295bc602154079e112a6d13","tid":1736521,"uid":318612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:23:17.000Z","msg":"Sorry借一借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家成日都話手足唔係condom,<br />\n咁我地聽朝一齊去支持佢地</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUHmpHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUHmpHa.jpg&h=8a668bc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76677029d53772377fd0298ed0350373dfbe9b5e","tid":1736521,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"877f14da33e98eda5a351c103cd2eb3a6b9428ba","tid":1736521,"uid":262043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"救人成本好大<br />\n大到成個運動既生死<br />\n如果依個運動輸咗<br />\n之前幾百個被檢控既手足就變condom"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:24:53.000Z","msg":"所以求大家唔好再陣地戰<br />\n唔好再屌散水撚"},{"pid":"f47826a8291df1b5874d6ed773815d03fd0fdb1b","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jb25RYt.png\" da