1:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d1543096070055e2bb5866285a11aa153d776f","tid":1736521,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:32:36.000Z","msg":"救人根本唔係呢幾日重點，重點係因為救人既心態，令大家突破咗好多心理關口<br />\n<br />\nPoly只係一個契機，點都要有一個原因激發大家"},{"pid":"651eb92a4978d77e58c7ddb1ce5bd56f0c7b0630","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:33:13.000Z","msg":"唔係要完全100%成功 先叫成功架咁多位<br />\n<br />\n要承認呢場係革命 戰爭<br />\n就要承認有失敗 係在所難免<br />\n今次知道唔可以再打陣地 下次就唔好再打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8dd0f279225b7f868f8885dd0e49fed987f8852","tid":1736521,"uid":306434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:33:28.000Z","msg":"召喚遙控土制魔法師。 由於對家講明會有狙擊手，擲火魔法/射箭/磚等等都可能被秒殺。<br />\n<br />\n只有SET陷阱，D狗一清場佔地就放遙距魔法。冇人知你身在何處。"},{"pid":"a4d26e3079769dece4a81e111b8b2c7d0444897d","tid":1736521,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0631f9d8df4787bcbcfba3d5ab93d6a4b9ee16ed","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76677029d53772377fd0298ed0350373dfbe9b5e","tid":1736521,"uid":336090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"877f14da33e98eda5a351c103cd2eb3a6b9428ba","tid":1736521,"uid":262043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"救人成本好大<br />\n大到成個運動既生死<br />\n如果依個運動輸咗<br />\n之前幾百個被檢控既手足就變condom"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:24:53.000Z","msg":"所以求大家唔好再陣地戰<br />\n唔好再屌散水撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"有人會話如果而家放棄 即刻當poly既人係condom<br />\n我覺得 如果大家為左救人 比人拉哂 場運動收埋皮<br />\n咁之前比人拉過既所有人 咪姐係變埋condom"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:34:42.000Z","msg":"老實講 唔好話我冷血 <br />\n我係Poly 人<br />\n但都係早幾日以為poly 唔守既撚屌<br />\n<br />\n無話condom 唔condom <br />\n你出得黎就真係有覺悟做義士<br />\n你係risk man 過<br />\n評估過自己合適個個職業先做架嘛<br />\n<br />\n唔通護士係疫區<br />\n當局話封鎖由你地死先後悔當初做護士？"},{"pid":"6a09ceeea42fa644807ccbb4fbfb8062e5ef79c0","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0665ae87c36d6369611c8f37cbfb5c06494bbb0a","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fb6289df58d63eee9ed0e682c223a2f13481ed","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08eb34a49ef67ac7d0c148cb34c886c7b99ad1c","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8ace08d55f7874cd617de12ceb16995e6f4d0e","tid":1736521,"uid":202895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:09:39.000Z","msg":"當有小小成功，成班人就想玩爛條橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個先係main point<br />\n<br />\n中大好彩成功一次<br />\n理大就唔掂<br />\n和你飛都係咁<br />\n<br />\n行動前可唔可以睇清楚環境，日子唔同，環境唔同<br />\n而仲有散水不可恥"},{"pid":"05cf28b5db627ce253b7a25ad240f2f2ec145981","tid":1736521,"uid":218097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}